All Classes

Class
Description
Agent
An interface for AI agents to play cathedral on CathedralGUI
Board
Class used to emulate a cathedral-board.
Building
The enum Building defines all possible builings in the game.
CathedralGUI
A GUI to run Cathedral games.
Color
The enum Color defines the colors a Building or an area can be colored.
Direction
The enum Direction describes the four cardinal directions a Building can be turned.
Game
Core class used to handle a full game of cathedral.
Placement
The immutable class Placement is used to take a turn in a Game.
Position
The class Position is a storage class for positions in a Game.
Turn
The class Turn is a storage class to store turns in a Game.
Turnable
The enum Turnable describes if a Building can be turned and has a different form in these Directions.
